high_descs: Go to the microwave above the stove, straight ahead of you.
Pull an apple out of the microwave.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator on your right.
Place the apple in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, between the egg and the tomato, wait a moment for the apple to chill, then remove the apple from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave above the stove, across from you.
Place the apple back in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward a bit, turn right, go in front of the stove
Open the microwave, pick up the apple in it, close the microwave
Turn around, go forward, turn right in front of the fridge
Put the apple in the fridge, wait, pick up the apple from the fridge
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the microwave
Put the apple in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Cool an apple and put it in the microwave

high_descs: Move to the left and forwards a bit, until you see the microwave above the stove.
Take out the apple that is inside of the microwave.
Turn completely around, walk forwards a bit, then turn right to face the fridge.
Chill the apple in the fridge before taking it back out and closing the doors.
Turn to the right and walk back over to the stove in front of you.
Place the apple in the microwave above the stove, to the right of the potato, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled apple to the microwave.
